title: The Afterlife - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/18/22
itunes:title: The Afterlife - Best of Coast to Coast AM - 7/18/22
description:
George Noory and psychic medium Rich Martini discuss his experiences contacting spirits from the other side, including Elvis Presley, comedian Bob Saget and Amelia Earhart, and how the death of a close friend led him to embrace his lifelong psychic abilities.
